{"tid":564552,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"拜年最驚就係老母喺親戚面前亂講野","createTime":"2018-02-18T06:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T06:58:36.000Z","uid":55851,"like":88,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9bbca940097a04ff21a3c8bbac4dbd6bb06fa194","tid":564552,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:16:14.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我本身好鐘意女僕，女僕服真係好好J，特別係低胸裝，對波唧晒出嚟，揸一揸短十年命都抵。<br />\n琴日去親戚屋企拜年，當然要老套地寒暄一番啦。 <br />\n傾傾下燒到我嗰個疊。<br />\n表姨：有咩興趣呀？<br />\n我笑笑口，都未諗到點答，我阿媽就已經搶住講：個衰仔好鐘意女傭架，D公仔放到全屋都係。<br />\n當下表姨全家人都目瞪口呆，就連本來喺廚房炒緊菜嘅菲律賓工人都忍唔住出廳擘大個口望住我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a968998d4549e66e4425e90744b816d5117c5a","tid":564552,"uid":28626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:19:34.000Z","msg":"你真識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d621513687160a6755593acc5dbd9273fce20e26","tid":564552,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62dd2d7086f09c155c3a85c3e213506254ff166","tid":564552,"uid":106633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:24:16.000Z","msg":"又幾好笑"},{"pid":"48f8093ad894a81d5387ddfe99e9c97127c44d7c","tid":564552,"uid":116466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:26:30.000Z","msg":"菲律賓工人係咪濕晒 求下集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f520b68d05f35679ddb524748ee88c83afcba9c","tid":564552,"uid":49918,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:26:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92fe77f9e8bfbadc7e77a872bd0d3c9a7944eede","tid":564552,"uid":1067,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T06:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/142711_9cc4b7